    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1938-01-22T00:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1938-01-22T00:00:00-05:00" n="311"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d311">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">793.94/12174: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul General at Shanghai</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gauss</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Shanghai</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1938-01-22T13:00:00+08:00"
                            >January 22, 1938—1 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 2:40 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>125. Reference my 1219, December 23, 9 p.m.,<note n="31" xml:id="d311fn31">
                        <ref target="frus1937v04#pg_409">
                            <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, 1937, Vol. <hi
                                rend="smallcaps">iv</hi>, p. 409</ref>.</note> and my 1255, December
                    31, noon<note n="32" xml:id="d311fn32">
                        <ref target="frus1937v04#pg_427">
                            <hi rend="italic">Ibid.</hi>, p. 427</ref>.</note> regarding Wuhu
                    incidents. Having received no further reply showing satisfactory action to
                    locate the military unit concerned, I have again brought the matter to the
                    attention of the Japanese Consul General asking that it be referred to his
                    military authorities for prompt and satisfactory action.</p>
                <p>Repeated to Hankow.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Gauss</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
